import React from 'react';
import { 
  Card, 
  CardContent, 
  Typography, 
  Grid, 
  Box,
  Chip,
  Avatar
} from '@mui/material';
import { TrendingUp, TrendingDown, AttachMoney, Business } from '@mui/icons-material';

const MainInfo: React.FC = () => {
  // Mock data - replace with actual data
  const companyData = {
    name: "TechCorp Inc.",
    ticker: "TECH",
    sector: "Technology",
    industry: "Software",
    marketCap: "$45.2B",
    sharePrice: "$156.78",
    priceChange: "+2.34%",
    volume: "12.5M",
    peRatio: "28.5",
    dividendYield: "1.2%",
    beta: "1.15"
  };

  return (
    <Card sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
      <CardContent>
        <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 3 }}>
          <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', mr: 2, width: 56, height: 56 }}>
            <Business fontSize="large" />
          </Avatar>
          <Box>
            <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
              {companyData.name} ({companyData.ticker})
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 1, flexWrap: 'wrap' }}>
              <Chip label={companyData.sector} color="primary" size="small" />
              <Chip label={companyData.industry} color="secondary" size="small" />
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Box>

        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" color="text.secondary">
                Share Price
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight="bold">
                {companyData.sharePrice}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
              <TrendingUp sx={{ color: 'success.main', mr: 1 }} />
              <Typography variant="body1" color="success.main">
                {companyData.priceChange}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                Market Cap
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight="500">
                {companyData.marketCap}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                Volume
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight="500">
                {companyData.volume}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                P/E Ratio
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight="500">
                {companyData.peRatio}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                Dividend Yield
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight="500">
                {companyData.dividendYield}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                Beta
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight="500">
                {companyData.beta}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                Sector
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight="500">
                {companyData.sector}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
};

export default MainInfo;
